page.title: 16Myself. Aaron Spicer.
page.content: I am eleven years old.I have a sister a mum and a dad.My mum works as a part time dentist.My dad works at a small builders.We have a family car.My dad and I support Manchester United Football Club.My hobbies are playing football and collecting football programmes.We live in an area of Reepham called Bircham Road.We live at ten.We have small lawns at the back and front of my house.I play with Howard quite a lot.Sometimes I go up to the recreation ground to play football with my dad and sometimes my friends come.My favourite films and T.V. programmes are Match of the Day,Where Eagles Dare,James Bond films,Manchester United playing a match on t.v.,and Coronation Street.My favourite foods are fish and chips, fillet steak,prawns,and bacon and eggs.
